    {
      "id": "PopularPost94416",
      "post_content": "Discarding a hand of 0 is perfectly valid and probably the best use of this card, the fact that this is causing so much confusion boggles my mind.  \n  \nSpells/abilities that involve your hand don't just fizzle if you have 0 cards, they interact with your hand and thus the 0 cards that are there.  \n  \nHave to discard a card? Discard nothing.  \nHave to reveal your hand? Reveal nothing.  \nHave to discard your hand? Discard nothing.  \nSomething checking hand size? It's a hand size of 0.  \n  \nIf a hand size of 0 ceased to be a hand then the whole Hellbent mechanic wouldn't work at all.  \n  \nIt's really as simple as that.",
      "posted_by": "doolydooly",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost94416\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_post\">Discarding a hand of 0 is perfectly valid and probably the best use of this card, the fact that this is causing so much confusion boggles my mind.<br/><br/>Spells/abilities that involve your hand don't just fizzle if you have 0 cards, they interact with your hand and thus the 0 cards that are there.<br/><br/>Have to discard a card? Discard nothing.<br/>Have to reveal your hand? Reveal nothing.<br/>Have to discard your hand? Discard nothing.<br/>Something checking hand size? It's a hand size of 0.<br/><br/>If a hand size of 0 ceased to be a hand then the whole Hellbent mechanic wouldn't work at all.<br/><br/>It's really as simple as that.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '94416'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy11428\">doolydooly</span>\r\n                                (8/9/2010 8:21:01 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl08_postRat